@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@plotId = demo_stage5_plot_example
@taskId = batch_example

### Dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/summary

### Dashboard plot list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/plots

### Dashboard plot detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/plots/{{plotId}}

### Dashboard heatmap
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/heatmap

### Dashboard disease statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/disease-statistics

### Dashboard latest records
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/latest-records?limit=10

### Dashboard latest alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/latest-alerts?limit=10

### Batch task status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
